Maintainer: Wenxuan Lu <wenxuanlu@hotmail.com>
Description: tlstractor implements TLS-Tractor for local ancestry–aware 
  genome-wide association studies (GWAS), integrating external GWAS summary 
  statistics with individual-level genotype data. It applies transfer learning 
  to improve the estimation of ancestry-specific effects while optionally 
  accounting for local ancestry.
